FBIS4-11281 "drlat080_a_94012" FBIS-LAT-94-080 Daily Report 23 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Outages To Spread Outages To Spread FL2304142494 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1000 GMT 23 Apr 94 FL2304142494 Havana Radio Progreso Network Spanish BFN [Text] Power outages could spread today in different parts of Cuba as the result of a breakdown that occurred at the Carlos Manuel de Cespedes thermoelectric power plant in Cienfuegos. The breakdown occurred in a line at that plant, and there is intense work going on with a view to solving the problem as quickly as possible, according to the Electric Union.
